%%{init: {'theme': 'forest'}}%%
sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor FW as Firmware
  participant API as Go API (device-open)
  participant DB as Postgres/Timescale

  FW->>API: GET /api/device-open/vfd?imei=...\n(or deviceUuid)
  API->>DB: Resolve device -> installation -> vfd_model_id
  DB-->>API: vfd model record(s)\nrs485 + command_dictionary + fault_map
  API-->>FW: 200 JSON vfdModels[]

  FW->>FW: Configure RS485 UART params\n(baud/parity/stopbits/slave_id)
  FW->>FW: Use command_dictionary for Modbus register writes\n+ realtime_parameters for reads
